<br />
I've come back to the Macintosh after abandoning it after graduating way back in 1989. I've had a G4 desktop and now a Powerbook G4 and only use my windows platform for gaming. To satisfy my gaming hobby I put up with windows but I see it solely as a means to an end. If I could run the games as they released and not have to wait for a random few to be converted to Mac OS X months if not years later I wouldn't hesitate to abandon microsoft windows.<br />
